data.description: 1 year temporary rate buydown if buyer uses sellers preferred lender for their financing! Discover the epitome of serene living in the heart of the Texas Hill Country! This fantastic 5 bedroom home in the 2023 MAX awards community of the year, Caliterra, presents an exquisite real estate opportunity, combining the allure of nature with the comforts of modern living.  Abundant upgrades throughout including a whole home air purifier, Dramatic curved staircase and 20' ceilings in the foyer and family room. Beautiful wood-look tile flows from room to room on the main level. A dedicated home office provides great separation from work and  home. The gourmet kitchen features a center island with seating, quartz countertops, and built-in stainless steel appliances including double ovens and a gas cooktop. The luxurious owner's suite offers a tray ceiling with crown molding plus a spa-like bathroom complete with dual vanities, garden tub and frameless glass shower. Additional bedroom downstairs, perfect for guests. Game and Media rooms on the second level with additional bedrooms and two full baths. This must-see home in the sought-after neighborhood has a space for everyone including a covered patio with outdoor kitchen, storage shed, and separate stone patio perfect for summer BBQs. Additional storage with spacious ceiling racks in the garage. Immerse yourself in the wonders of nature as you explore the extensive network of hiking and biking trails, kayak rentals, 3 fishing ponds living the Hill Country lifestyle with a multitude of other amenities plus all the nearby wineries, breweries and boutique shopping that Dripping Springs has to offer!
